steps.name: When Web app login using customerLoginCrendentails
Then Verify that user successfully redirected on homepage
When I click on the second index link Master
When I click on the second index link Vaccine Type
Then Search and delete duplicate data Auto_Test_Vaccine
When User click on the button text New Vaccine Type
Then It redirects on the New Vaccine Type screen
When I click on the button with text Create
Then validation message Please Enter CVX Code appears
Then validation message Please Enter Name appears
Then validation message Please Select Status appears
When I fill 12300 data in cvx code field
When I fill Auto_Test_Vaccine data in vaccine Name field
When I fill Healthcare data in brand Name field
When I fill The Auto_Test_Vaccine vaccine is designed to protect's from the virus. data in description field
When I fill Consult the doctor before using this vaccine. data in note field
When I fill Active data in status field
When I fill Test@123 data in internal ID field
When I fill True data in non vaccine field
When I fill 12300 data in update date field
When I fill Yes data in favourite field
When I click on the button with text Create
Then Success message Vaccine Type Added Succesfully! appears
When I populate data Auto_Test_Vaccine in the "Search" field

Then "Vaccine type" details should be visible in the list with 12300 and Healthcare and Auto_Test_Vaccine and The Auto_Test_Vaccine vaccine is designed to protect's from the virus. and Consult the doctor before using this vaccine. and Active and Test@123 and True and Yes and <date>
When User click on the button text New Vaccine Type
Then It redirects on the New Vaccine Type screen
When I fill 12300 data in cvx code field
When I fill Auto_Test_Vaccine data in vaccine Name field
When I fill Active data in status field
When I click on the button with text Create
Then validation message Please Enter a Unique CVX Code appears
Then validation message Please Enter a Unique Vaccine Name appears
When I click on the button with text Close
Then New Vaccine Type popup should be closed successfully
